         <div xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838"><!-- p2l6-r8 -->
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Hd1e108">Rubrica 8</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De iudicibus et iudiciis</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e114">
              <lb ed="#K" n="57"/>De iudicibus et iudiciis. Rubrica. 8.
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e119">
              <lb ed="#K"/> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e115">exodo c. 23.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e123">Non declinabis 
              <lb ed="#K"/>in iudicio pauperis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e140"> 
              <lb ed="#K"/> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e127">leuitico. c. 19.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e142">Non facies quod iniquum est: 
              <lb ed="#K"/>nec iniuste iudicabis. Noli<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>te 
              facere iniquum aliquod in 
              <lb ed="#K"/>iudicio: in regula: in pondere: in 
              <lb ed="#K"/>mensura: statera iusta et equa sint po<lb ed="#K" n="1" break="no"/>ndera:
                <pb ed="#K" n="95-r"/>
                <cb ed="#K" n="a"/>
              iustus modius: equus<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>que 
              sextarius.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e159">
              <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e149">24 c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e161">Equum iu<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>dicium 
              sit inter vos: siue peregri<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>nis: 
              siue ciuis peccauerit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e169">
              <lb ed="#K"/> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e164">Moyses in deuteronomio. c. 27.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e173">Male<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>dictus 
              qui peruertit iudicium ad<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>uene 
              et pupilli et vidue.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e181">
              <lb ed="#K"/> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e178">Psalmista pslamus. 57.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e185">Si vere vtique iustiti<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>am 
              loquimini: recte iudicate filii 
              <lb ed="#K"/>hominum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e191">
              <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e188">105 psalmus.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e193">Beati qui custo<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>diunt 
              iudicium et faciunt iusti<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>tiam 
              omni tempore.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e201">
              <lb ed="#K"/> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e203">Salomon in prouerb. ca. 6.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e205">Ne declines ad de<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>xteram 
              neque ad finistram.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e212">
              <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e215">17. c.</ref> 
              <lb ed="#K"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e214">Qui iustificat impium: et qui condemnat 
              <lb ed="#K"/>iustum abominabilis est vterque 
              <lb ed="#K"/>apud deum</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e222">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e228">26 c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e224">Iudicium de<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>terminat 
               causas.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e230">
              <lb ed="#K"/> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e240">Isaias propheta ca. 5.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e234">Uhe qui iustificatis impium 
              <lb ed="#K"/>pro muneribus: et iustitiam 
              <lb ed="#K"/>iusti au feritis ab eo.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e242">
              <lb ed="#K"/> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e254">Aristoteles rethoricorum libro 2. c. 18.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e246">Iudex 
              <lb ed="#K"/>est qui in ciuilibus concertationibus 
              <lb ed="#K"/>inquisita iudicat</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e252">
              <lb ed="#K"/> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e266">Iesus filius sirach in ecc. c. 5.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e256">Iustifica pusil<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>lum 
              et magnum similiter.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e262">
              <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e276">18. c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e264">Ante 
              <lb ed="#K"/>iudicium praepara iustitiam tibi.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e271">
              <lb ed="#K"/> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e288">Pylon in li. sapientie. c. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e275">Diligi<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>te 
              iustitiam qui iudicatis terram.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e281">
              <lb ed="#K"/> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e301">Oratius odarum li. 2. c. 58.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e285">Quotiens bonus atque 
              <lb ed="#K"/>fidus Iudex honestum pretulit 
              <lb ed="#K"/>vtili Reiecit alta dona 
              <lb ed="#K"/>nocentium Uultu: per obstantes ca<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>teruas
              Explicuit sua vic<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>tor 
              arma.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e297">
              <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e319">Idem in sermonibus 
                  <cb ed="#K" n="b"/>
              <lb ed="#K"/>li. 2. ser. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e301">Male verum examinat 
              <lb ed="#K"/>omnis Corruptus iudex.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e309">
              <lb ed="#K"/> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e332">Tullius de legibus li. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e313">Quid 
              <lb ed="#K"/>magnificentius quam posse de<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>cernere 
              vt magistratum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e319">
              <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e342">Idem de 
              <lb ed="#K"/>oratore li. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e321">Plura multo ho<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>mines 
              iudicant odio aut amo<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>re: 
              aut cupiditate: aut iracundia 
              <lb ed="#K"/>aut dolore: aut letitia: aut spe: 
              <lb ed="#K"/>aut timore: aut errore: aut aliqua 
              <lb ed="#K"/>permotione mentis quam iudicii 
              <lb ed="#K"/>formula: aut legibus.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e338">
              <lb ed="#K"/> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e365">Oratius de tristibus li. i. c. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e342">Iudic<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>is 
              officium est vt res: ita tempora 
              <lb ed="#K"/>rerum Querere.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e349">
              <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e379">Idem de ponto 
              <lb ed="#K"/>li. 2. e. 9. et antepenultima.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e353">Conspic<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>itur 
              nunquam meliore 
              <lb ed="#K"/>potentia causa Quam quotiens 
              <lb ed="#K"/>vanas non sinit esse pr<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>eces.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e367">
              <lb ed="#K"/> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e400">Quintilianus declam. 12 declam.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e371">Nos ideo 
              <lb ed="#K"/>magistratus legibusque amo<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>ribus 
              nostris accepimus: ne 
              <lb ed="#K"/>sui quisque doloris iudex 
              <lb ed="#K"/>sit: et assidue scelerum cau<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>se 
              se refellant si vltio 
              <lb ed="#K"/>imitabitur crimen. Si ad ar<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>ma 
              mittimur et instituitur per<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>niciosa 
              nocendi contentio et 
              <lb ed="#K"/>in vicem leges ira succedat: 
              <lb ed="#K"/>premetur quidem innoxia in<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>firmitas:
               et paucorum dominio sub<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>iecta 
               plebs triste seruitium perferet.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e392">
               
              <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e427">Mattheus in euangel. c. 7.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e396">In quo iudicio
        iudicaueritis: iudicabimini: et in qua mensu
        ra mensi fueritis: remecietur vobis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e404">
               
              <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e441">Ioannes in euangelio. c. 7.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e408">Nolite iudicare
        secundum faciem sed iustum iudicium iudicate.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e414">
               
              <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e453">Iacobus in epistola vnica. c. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e418">Iudicium sine
        misericordia ei qui non fecit misericordiam: su
        perexaltat autem misericordia iudicio</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e426">
               
              <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e467">Seneca tragediarum in medea. c. 4.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e430">Qui sta
        tuit aliquid parte inaudita altera:
        Equum licet statuerit haud equus fuit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e439">
               
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e481">Idem de tranquillitate animi:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e443">Semper in iudicio
        fauor efficit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e449">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e492">Idem de clementia:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e451">Prope
        est vt libenter damnet qui cito: prope est vt ini
        micos puniat qui nimis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e459">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e504">Idem in prouerb.</ref>
        <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e461">Ad penitendum properat: qui cito iudicat.
        In iudicando criminosa est celeritas.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e469">
               
              <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e517">Ptolomeus in centiloquio. c. 12.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e473">Beni
        uolentia et maliuolentia hominem in iudiciis
        errare faciunt.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e481">
               
              <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e531">Lex diges. ti. de orig. iur. l. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e485">Per eos qui
        iurisdictioni praesunt effectus iuris accipitur.
        Quantum est enim eius in ciuitate esse: nisi sint
        qui iura regere possint.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e495">
               
              <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e547">Lex codi. ti. de iudeis. l. nullus:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e499">Iccirco iu
        diciorum vigor iurisque publici tutela videtur in
        medio constituta ne quisquam sibiipsi permittere
        valeat vltionem.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e510">
               
              <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e563">Ambrosius de officiis lib. 2. c. 24.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e514">In iudi
        cio gratia absit causa merita decernant.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e520">
               
              <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e576">Claudianus li. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e524">Merent captiue: pollute
        iudice leges.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e530">
               
              <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e588">Cato. c. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e534">Equum iudica.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e538">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e596">Capitulo. 2.</ref>
        <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e540">Esto forti animo: cum sis damnatus inique. <!--140.xml-->
        <cb ed="#V" n="b"/>
                  Nemo diu gaudet: sub iniquo iudice vin
        cens.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e554">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e613"><sic>Cupitulo.</sic> 4.</ref>
        <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e556">Iudicis auxilium: sub iniquo teste rogato.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e562">
               
              <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e626">Cassiodorus epistolarum li. i. e. 3.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e566">Facilis recti
        persuasor est innocens iudex. Excessus tunc sunt
        in formidine cum creduntur iudicibus displice
        re.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e577">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e640">Li. 3. e. 7.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e579">Tamdium iudex dicitur quamdiu
        iustus putatur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e585">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e651">36 e.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e587">In causis semper est su
        specta potentia.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e593">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e661">39. e.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e595">Inumbrat famam
        publicam in consule tenacitatis obscuritas.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e601">
               
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e673">Li. 4. e. 10.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e605">Quid a bellica confusione pax
        tranquilla distabit: si per vim litigia terminen
        tur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e613">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e685">28 e.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e615">Dignus est inter alios sequen
        da decernere qui sibi modum visus est legitti
        me conuersationis imponere.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e623">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e697">Li. 6 epi. 4</ref>
        <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e625">Est nimirum magnum et <sic>sigulare</sic> praeconium si iudi
        ces non accipiant vbi sunt qui multum dare con
        tendunt.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e636">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e712">12. e.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e638">Prima equitas est a se praesu
        les inchoare: vt timeant criminosi quem ne
        queunt similem reperire. Nullas enim in se cul
        pas timet reus quas habere respexit cogni
        torem. Si vos actus nullus damnat in altero
        quia natura est humani animi vt nitatur par
        cius vindicare quod se cognouerit amisisse.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e655">
               
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e736">Libro. 8. e. 4.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e659">Tales decet esse aulicos vi
        ros vt nature bona iudicio frontis aperiant:
        vt possint aguosci de moribus dum videntur.
        Tacens enim plerumque despicabilis est: etsi eum
        lingua nobilitat.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e671">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e752">15. e.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e673">Gloria regni est re
        perisse iudices exquisitos. Auari iudices ne
        sciunt quantum delinquunt. Nam cum vendunt a
        liena crimina sua faciunt esse peccata.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e683">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e766">Lib.
        9. e. 9.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e685">Non minus est malum bellicum vitasse:
        quam seua discussionis euadere. Ipsa est vera
        securitas que de nulla iudicis iniquitate for
        midat.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e697">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e783">19. epi.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e699">Metus cuncta disponit: si
        reus crimen in iudicante non inuenit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e705">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e793">Lib.
        10. e. 6.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e707">Cui iustitia committitur malis moribus
        non grauetur: alioquin inefficax est ab homine
        exigere quod agnoscitur non habere.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e718">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e808">19. epi</ref>
        <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e720">Illa sunt vera iudicia vbi neminem compri
        mit vlla timiditas.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e728">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e820">Libro. 11. e. 9.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e730">Inuti
        le bonum est iudicem non accipere: et multis acci
        piendi licentiam praebuisse.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e738">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e832">33 e.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e740">Non est he
        sitationis metus vbi non est iudicis venalis <!--141.xml-->
        <pb ed="#V" n="57-v"/>
                  <cb ed="#V" n="a"/>
                  auditus.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e754">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e850">Libro. 12. et fi. e. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e756">Quam periculo
        sum est pati iudicem rationabiliter iratu: et illum de
        fortunis tuis decernere quam te constat grauitur irritasse</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e764">
               
              <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e864">Isidorus soliloquiorum lib. i. ca. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e768">Petit le
        ges auaritia iudicante. Premia et dona legi
        bus vires tulerunt. Ubique pecunia vincit.
        Ubique venale iudicium est.</quote> 
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e776">
            <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e878">Lib. 2. c. 41.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e778">An
        cipitem dium deliberat sententiam. Nullum iudices su
        spitionis arbitrio: ante proba. et sic iudica. Peri
        culosum est quempiam de suspitione iudicare.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e785">
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e787"> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e894">49
        c.</ref>Munera sepe veritatem praeuaricant. Cito vio
        latur auro iustitia: cito corrumpitur munere.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e796">
               
              <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e908">Auctor libri qui dicitur facetus. c. 8.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e800">Qua
        lis erit iudex: tales sunt quippe ministri
        Si malus est osis: fit populusque malus.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e808">
               
              <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e922">Gualterius de castellione li. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e812">Si lis inci
        derit: te iudice dirige libram
        Iudicii: nec flectat amor: nec munera palpent
        Nec moueat stabilem persone acceptio mentem.
        Cum semel obtinuit vitiorum mater in aula
        Pestis auaritie: que sola incarcerat omnes
        Uirtutum species: spreto moderamine iuris.
        Curritur in facinus nec leges curia curat.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e831">
               
              <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e947">Montenarius in luna cleri. c. 108</ref>
        <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e835">Iudex qui perimit scelerum fomenta: minister
        Noscitur esse dei: qui vero negligit hostis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e843">
               
              <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e960">Prouerb. metrice extraor. li. vagam.</ref>
        <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e847">Quattuor ista: metus: odium: dilectio: census:
        Sepe solent hominum: rectos peruertere sensus.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-d1e855">
               
              <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Rd1e973">Prouerb. vulgar.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d42838-Qd1e859">Chi a pare zuse per se
        gur o va apleo. Rason per amore perde valore</quote>
            </p>
